# The Question

Every dynamical prediction in this framework is off by 0.27%:
- α × ln(m_Pl/m_e) = 0.376017 vs. 3/8 = 0.375000 → 0.27%
- sin²θ_W(GUT) = α × ln = 0.376017 vs. 3/8 = 0.375000 → same 0.27%
